    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/f760ee8b20077f9322dac2f829520233.poster.avif?t=1767962259\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/f760ee8b20077f9322dac2f829520233.webm?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/f760ee8b20077f9322dac2f829520233.mp4?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>20年前的大火灾使得几乎整个世界都陷入了火海, 带来了空前的生物灭绝和地球毁坏. 只有30%的人类幸存了下来, 而且全都集中在地球上为数不多的区域中. 随着政府倒台, 神秘公司接管了控制权. 整个世界正陷入混乱和无政府状态. 欢迎来到1998年纽约.<br><br>你是一名未来世界的赏金猎人. 你的主要目标是收集精魂 – 一种存储着植入者信息并能够控制植入者的生物芯片. 这些芯片由统治着新地球的某家巨头所研制. 没有精魂, 意味着任何人都将不复存在.<br><br><br><strong>由玩家驱动的剧情</strong><br>如何接近你的目标将取决于你. 你的选择不仅将影响故事的发展 – 它还能够让你以自己喜欢的方式来应对各种情况. 你的决定将影响大量可重复体验的故事情节.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/b21e714e1b791418f3f39b8ec77bb225.poster.avif?t=1767962259\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/b21e714e1b791418f3f39b8ec77bb225.webm?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/b21e714e1b791418f3f39b8ec77bb225.mp4?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索广袤的开放世界</strong><br>ExeKiller的世界美丽又致命. 从沙漠到峡谷, 危机四伏的高速公路和辐射场, 你将勇往直前, 穿越不同的地区.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/add5734741685ad38783176cd43ca313.poster.avif?t=1767962259\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/add5734741685ad38783176cd43ca313.webm?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/add5734741685ad38783176cd43ca313.mp4?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>追捕法外狂徒</strong><br>你可以选择杀死他们, 将其绳之以法或者选择释放 – 完全由你决定. 充分利用环境和各种类型的武器, 工具. 使用你的技能来占据上风. 偷偷躲开敌人或者按照自己的方式来摆脱困境.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/5355b1c9fe45e821e8e9718322565769.poster.avif?t=1767962259\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/5355b1c9fe45e821e8e9718322565769.webm?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/5355b1c9fe45e821e8e9718322565769.mp4?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>不断变化的环境</strong><br>在令人惊叹的昼夜轮回, 动态天气以及辐射太阳风暴的末世景观中体验一段难以忘怀的旅程.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/e3beae5ba17304c69b79d218b6b6a9a9.poster.avif?t=1767962259\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/e3beae5ba17304c69b79d218b6b6a9a9.webm?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701840/extras/e3beae5ba17304c69b79d218b6b6a9a9.mp4?t=1767962259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
